All Packages

Package Summary
Package
Description
application.classes
Contains static classes that contain constant information.
application.client
It contains all java and fxml files that are used to manage the client part of the program.
application.client.controllers
Contains static classes that manage the interactions of the graphical interface and its configuration.
application.client.controllers.clubStaff
Contains static classes that manage the interactions of the graphical interface and its configuration of club staff.
application.client.controllers.partner
Contains static classes that manage the interactions of the graphical interface and its configuration of partners.
application.client.managers
Contains all the classes that deal with managing client data.
application.client.views
Contains all the program's fxml files.
application.client.views.clubStaff
Contains all the club staff's fxml files.
application.client.views.partner
Contains all the partner's fxml files.
application.communications
It contains all the classes that are used for communication between client and server.
application.models
Contains all the classes that represent the data models.
application.server
Contains the files used to manage the server part of the program.
application.server.managers
Contains all partner singletons used by the server to process and manage data.
test
It contains all the files useful for testing the program.
test.classes
Contains the test classes from the classes package.
test.client
Contains the test classes from the client package.
test.client.managers
Contains the test classes of the client managers package.
test.communications
Contains the test classes of communications package.
test.models
Contains the test classes of the models package.
test.server
Contains the test classes of the server package.
test.server.managers
Contains the test classes of the server manager package.
